videos.description: Murray State's Ja Morant posterizes a defender on the fast break as he elevates to throw down a vicious one-handed jam.
videos.headline: Morant throws down vicious one-handed dunk in traffic

videos.headline: Eastern Illinois' Kukobat finishes alley-oop
